<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id778989f1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s423a"><num value="423a">§ 423a.</num><heading> Acceptance of donations of lands</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Interior is authorized to accept, on behalf of the United States, donations of lands, interests therein, or rights pertaining thereto required for the Petersburg National Battlefield.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id778989f2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1926-07-03/ch746/s2">July 3, 1926, ch. 746, § 2</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/44/822">44 Stat. 822</ref>; Ex. Ord. No. 6166, § 2, <date date="1933-06-10">June 10, 1933</date>; Ex. Ord. No. 6228, § 1, <date date="1933-07-28">July 28, 1933</date>; <ref href="/us/pl/87/603/s1">Pub. L. 87–603, § 1</ref>, <date date="1962-08-24">Aug. 24, 1962</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/76/403">76 Stat. 403</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id778989f3-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id778989f4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I78" topic="changeOfName" id="id778989f5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">Change of Name</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">“Petersburg National Battlefield” substituted in text for “Petersburg National Military Park” pursuant to <ref href="/us/pl/87/603">Pub. L. 87–603</ref>. See <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s423h–1">section 423h–1 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="execDoc" id="id778989f6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Executive Documents</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I85" topic="transferOfFunctions" id="id778989f7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">Transfer of Functions</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Transfer of administrative functions of park, see note set out under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s423">section 423 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
